						<div class="postbody">Knowing the logic involved in generating the CLK pulse sent to the controller ports would help. /OE1 and /OE2 might be involved, though it's hard to imagine that the DMA disconnects those (seemingly unrelated) signals as well. The wiki could also be wrong, and we might be misremembering the effects of the conflict.</div>

