						<div class="postbody">If a $4016 read is triggered on r4016 going low, then it would ignore successive reads because r4016 stays low for the entire duration (it does not toggle with phi2):<br /><br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.qmtpro.com/~nes/chipimages/visual2a03/index.html?a=00&amp;d=a20f8e10408e1340e88e1540eaeaeaa296eaeacad0fba6004c8000&amp;a=80&amp;d=eaeaeaeaad164010fe30fe">http://www.qmtpro.com/~nes/chipimages/v ... 4010fe30fe</a><!-- m --><br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent"><br />cyc&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ab&nbsp; db rw&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;pc&nbsp; &nbsp;a&nbsp; x&nbsp; y&nbsp; s&nbsp; &nbsp; p&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; r4016<br />=======================================================================<br />1398&nbsp; &nbsp; 0084 ad 1 LDA&amp;nbsp;Abs&nbsp; 0084 00 a2 00 bd Nv&amp;#8209BdIzc&nbsp; &nbsp;1&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;- LDA $4016 <br />1399&nbsp; &nbsp; 0084 ad 1 LDA&amp;nbsp;Abs&nbsp; 0084 00 a2 00 bd Nv&amp;#8209BdIzc&nbsp; &nbsp;1 <br />1399&nbsp; &nbsp; 0085 16 1&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;0085 00 a2 00 bd Nv&amp;#8209BdIzc&nbsp; &nbsp;1 <br />1400&nbsp; &nbsp; 0085 16 1&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;0085 00 a2 00 bd Nv&amp;#8209BdIzc&nbsp; &nbsp;1<br />1400&nbsp; &nbsp; 0086 40 1&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;0086 00 a2 00 bd Nv&amp;#8209BdIzc&nbsp; &nbsp;1<br />1401&nbsp; &nbsp; 0086 40 1&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;0086 00 a2 00 bd Nv&amp;#8209BdIzc&nbsp; &nbsp;1<br />1401&nbsp; &nbsp; 4016 00 1&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;0087 00 a2 00 bd Nv&amp;#8209BdIzc&nbsp; &nbsp;0&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;- DMA halt<br />1402&nbsp; &nbsp; 4016 00 1&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;0087 00 a2 00 bd Nv&amp;#8209BdIzc&nbsp; &nbsp;0<br />1402&nbsp; &nbsp; 4016 00 1&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &